Sixty-sixth Avenue (White Pot Road) north side, in line of Alderton Street, showing in three views the Springsteen house. Michael S. Springsteen (b.1804 d.1886) erected this house in 1859. His son David who married Anna W. Monfort of Brooklyn inherited it. He died about 1912. His widow sold it in 1928.

May 1923
View 2: April 1923
View 3: July 1923
